{"tid":914434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"田徑教練被控非禮學員脫罪 團體憂受害人怕證據不足噤聲","createTime":"2018-11-24T09:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T03:23:56.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c9a883b47ca873e9166bcead2374fd2b0a750793","tid":914434,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T09:22:51.000Z","msg":"女性反性侵運動#Metoo席捲全球，其中香港1名田徑教練被控10年前非禮女學員案，轟動全港，惟法庭近日判教練非禮罪名不成立。香港性教育研究及治療專業協會委員、家庭醫生吳穎英稱，尊重法庭判決，但憂慮判決在觀感上，會令其他受害者怕不夠證據而噤聲，建議市民如身邊朋友主動剖白性侵經歷，應聆聽對方並給予認同，幫助對方講出經歷。<br />\n此外，香港性教育研究及治療專業協會於2015年11月至2016年4月，以問卷調查訪問441名女性，當中12%人稱童年時曾被性侵犯。調查發現，曾被性侵女子在性抑鬱、焦慮和害怕層面的指數，均較其他受訪女子高。協會引述文獻指，如3項指數偏高，容易引致性功能障礙，難與伴侶建立親密性關係。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181124/large/1543044665_55ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181124%2Flarge%2F1543044665_55ae.jpg&h=2d52e800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181124/58952723\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181124%2F58952723&d=jvvzT6rx31Fn0FjFXWvsldibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=130139e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181124%2F58952723&h=e3ce8b19\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181124/58952723</a>"},{"pid":"3845f02d46c2a8ed3ea8a442a2ce6aabd00dc0c1","tid":914434,"uid":128928,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T09:38:04.000Z","msg":"其實係呂麗瑤案入面，邊個係受害人？<br />\n個教練定個學生妹？<br />\n我好亂"},{"pid":"75f1fb38489ec184fe12662b0a4c27d821edd39a","tid":914434,"uid":38194,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T10:41:07.000Z","msg":"好心啲女權撚就收爹啦，由始至終最邪惡就係佢哋"},{"pid":"2366d48091fc252a0c3217b7b87170f787f650e2","tid":914434,"uid":18479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy